These are Puzzles for 3x7 Level 2

.:: Puzzle 3x7-Level-2-1::.
7 different games are played: go, chess, domino, billiard, backgammon, canasta, poker
There are 7 different favourite beverages: soy-milk, mirinda, lemonade, cola, iced-tea, hot-chocolate, milk
The people use 7 different means of transport: train, helicopter, jet-ski, skateboard, motorbike, subway, ship
 1. the person playing backgammon is on the far left##1
 2. the person driving the helicopter is on the left of the person playing go##1
 3. the person driving the ship is between the person drinking mirinda and the person drinking soy-milk##2
 4. the person playing billiard is on the left of the person driving the subway##1
 5. the person drinking mirinda is on the left of the person playing chess##1
 6. the person playing go is the person driving the ship##1
 7. the person drinking cola is between the person driving the skateboard and the person playing backgammon##2
 8. the person driving the motorbike is on the left of the person driving the subway##1
 9. the person driving the subway is on the left of the person driving the train##1
10. the person playing poker is the person drinking lemonade##1
11. the person drinking hot-chocolate is the person playing billiard##1
12. the person playing poker is on the left of the person playing domino##1
13. the person driving the train is the person drinking iced-tea##1
14. the person playing canasta is between the person driving the jet-ski and the person driving the ship##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |     2      |     3      |    4     |   5    |     6      |    7     |
| Game   | backgammon | go     | canasta | chess | billiard | poker  | domino  |
| Beverage   | soy-milk  | cola        | mirinda  | milk     | hot-chocolate   | lemonade       | iced-tea   |
| Transport         | helicopter   | ship | skateboard    | jet-ski  | motorbike | subway | train |

