.:: Puzzle 3x7-Level-2-2::.
7 different brands of cigars are smoked: tiparillo, fonseca, prince, bluemaster, ritmeester, aristoff, havana
There 7 different types of food: spinach, orange, raspberry, tomato, mango, cabbage, potato
The people have 7 different jobs:  paramedic, scientist, electrician, analyst, entrepreneur, architect, firefighter
 1. the fonseca-smoker is on the right of the scientist##1
 2. the person eating mango is the person eating mango##1
 3. the person eating mango is on the right of the person eating tomato##1
 4. the person eating tomato is on the left of the paramedic##1
 5. the person eating spinach is the havana-smoker##1
 6. the tiparillo-smoker is the analyst##1
 7. the tiparillo-smoker is between the person eating potato and the firefighter##2
 8. the person eating raspberry is on the left of the ritmeester-smoker##1
 9. the person eating potato is on the left of the person eating tomato##1
10. the prince-smoker is on the right of the entrepreneur##1
11. the ritmeester-smoker is on the right of the tiparillo-smoker##1
12. the paramedic is the fonseca-smoker##1
13. the bluemaster-smoker is on the left of the tiparillo-smoker##1
14. the bluemaster-smoker is on the right of the architect##1
15. the fonseca-smoker is on the far right##1
16. the person eating orange is on the left of the havana-smoker##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |     2     |      3       |    4     |   5    |     6     |    7     |
| Cigar   | aristoff | havana      | bluemaster     | tiparillo  | ritmeester | prince | fonseca |
| Food         | orange  | spinach | cabbage | raspberry | potato | tomato   | mango  |
| Job     | electrician   | architect     | firefighter        | analyst  | entrepreneur   | scientist       | paramedic      |

