7 different pets are kept: rabbit, hedgehog, turtle, hamster, horse, dog, rat
7 different brands of cigars are smoked: oliveros, davidoff, cain, blend, montecristo, bluemaster, tiparillo
 1. the davidoff-smoker is the owner of the rabbit##1
 2. the montecristo-smoker is the owner of the hamster##1
 3. the blend-smoker is on the right of the owner of the horse##1
 4. the cain-smoker is the person who's sport is soccer##1
 5. the bluemaster-smoker is between the tiparillo-smoker and the owner of the rat##2
 6. the montecristo-smoker is on the right of the oliveros-smoker##1
 7. the person who's sport is biathlon is on the left of the person who's sport is sailing##1
 8. the cain-smoker is on the left of the owner of the rat##1
 9. the tiparillo-smoker is on the far right##1
10. the owner of the turtle is on the right of the owner of the dog##1
11. the davidoff-smoker is the owner of the rabbit##1
12. the owner of the turtle is on the right of the person who's sport is skateboarding##1
13. the person who's sport is climbing is on the left of the owner of the hamster##1
14. the tiparillo-smoker is the person who's sport is cricket##1
15. the oliveros-smoker is on the left of the person who's sport is biathlon##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1      |     2      |     3      |    4    |      5       |    6     |    7     |
