The people prefer 7 different music-genres: trance, hip-hop, dubstep, country, gospel, techno, rock
 1. the fan gospel is on the far left##1
 2. the person who's birthday is in july is the person playing chess##1
 3. the fan dubstep is the person who's birthday is in february##1
 4. the person who's birthday is in december is on the far right##1
 5. the fan trance is on the right of the person playing poker##1
 6. the person playing go is on the far right##1
 7. the person playing canasta is in the middle##1
 8. the person who's birthday is in february is on the left of the person who's birthday is in july##1
 9. the fan techno is the person who's birthday is in april##1
10. the fan trance is the person playing billiard##1
11. the person who's birthday is in january is the fan rock##1
12. the person playing whist is the fan gospel##1
13. the fan country is on the far right##1
14. the person who's birthday is in november is between the person who's birthday is in january and the person who's birthday is in february##2
15. the person playing bridge is on the right of the person who's birthday is in july##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |     2     |    3     |    4    |     5      |     6      |     7     |
